ion with SS and what zone are they in.  thanks ahead of time <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukayleighdrake.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KayleighDrake</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/13/01 10:46:43 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> Kill giants of course.<br>
<br>
However I'm not sure you realize that to do the SS quest, you need drops from the Halls of Testing in the Temple of Veeshan. They're not exactly easy to get, and the chain is the rarest drop. At 54 it's not going to be easy to get your hands on that stuff. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umanbass.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Manbass</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/13/01 12:45:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> On the 7th hammer, in my experience, silk and leather are the rarest drops.  Our Plate and chain wearers are moslty in full SS. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urazuuk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Razuuk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/17/01 8:12:08 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> Kael armor you can get with 1 group up in the arena, rare drops, but possible. <br>
<br>
To get SS armor you need a guild type bunch of people, around 18 at least, with some high level ok equiped warriors (defensive is very useful). Drops in ToV are fairly common, you see a drop every 5 kills or less i find. <br>
<br>
So without a good guild, you aint getting SS armor, cept if you ebay *cough*  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubraidfreak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>braidfreak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 9:32:51 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> or you could just buy the MQ from someone.  our guild has a bankful of extra ToV drops that we don't need and we sell it off for multi-quest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udemerdar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Demerdar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/dagger.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 3:40:33 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> I've been to HoT(Halls of Testing) in ToV(Temple of Veeshan) and from what i've seen, these are what i find from most common, to least common drops.  Plate, chain, leather, silk.  Even though I don't play anymore...I believe thats what the order was. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uverocity.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Verocity</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/20/01 8:53:51 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> Aye, Silk is the rarest unfortunately.  We raid HOT once a week and we start early.  I have to say that, number of drops seem connected to the number of people in the zone.  When we were there alone(5 groups), we were getting insane drops.  1 out of 3.  As the day rolled on and more guilds showed up, it droped to like 1 in 7-8.  Just my observation.  I don't know if it possible to link treasure with zone population but who knows. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugilimisilverwing.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gilimi Silverwing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/20/01 9:20:03 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> HoT is 1 groupable. You dont *need* 18 people. It just eliminates alot of downtime (assuming your efficient)<br>
<br>
Ive done it like this for over a month now. Druid cleric shaman tank rogue monk/bard, and my gimp ench sitting out for speed and tash. <br>
<br>
The drops are random, and dont vary by number of people. Ive been there with 6, and gotten 2/3 drops off the first 3 mobs, then more drops after that, for a total of 15 drops in 4 hours. Then other times, maybe 1 or 2 drops in 4 hours.<br>
<br>
Its Random.<br>
<br>
Mind your Plate, Chain, Leather, Silk. Is the decending order of commonality.<br>
<br>
Gilimi Silverwing<br>
60 Warlord<br>
Saryrn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/untingearreaver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ntin Gearreaver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/21/01 1:01:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SS Armor quests help</span><hr size=1> Seems to me its Plate, Leather, Silk, Chain. I been on lots of raids with no chain drops but half sets of silk and leathers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3302.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3327.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3270.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=3270.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3270.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3270.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jum